<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Islamabad, May 10 (XINHUA) -- All Pak-China 
Friendship Association hosted a reception here tonight to 
celebrate the 40th anniversary of the founding of Chinese 
People's Association for Friendship With Foreign Countries 
