friend of Pakistan," said Ambassador Zhou Gang. 
  "it is the steadfast policy of the Chinese Government to 
further cement and develop friendship and cooperation with 
Pakistan," he added. 
  CPAFFC, as a non-governmental organization founded in 1954, 
has established contacts and relations of friendship and 
cooperation with more than 100 organizations in over 90 
countries. 

