<F P=100> Central-South Region </F>
<H3> <TI>   Henan's Zhengzhou Promotes Treasury Bond Sales </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Henan's Zhengzhou Promotes Treasury Bond Sales </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   HK1005131694 Zhengzhou Henan People's Radio Network in 
Mandarin 1030 GMT 6 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> HK1005131694 </F>
<F P=104>  Zhengzhou Henan People's Radio Network </F>
<F P=105>  Mandarin </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] By 1 May, the city of Zhengzhou had sold 380 
million yuan worth of treasury bonds, including 60 million yuan 
worth of two-year bonds and 320 million yuan worth of three-year 
bonds. 
  Zhengzhou party and government leaders have attached 
importance to promoting the sales of treasury bonds this year. 
On 30 March, the city government held a special mobilization 
meeting to promote treasury bond sales. Quotas were assigned 
and the responsibilities of relevant units were defined. 
Various relevant units responsible for selling treasury bonds 
have taken strengthening service and providing convenience for 
buyers as their guideline to make early and full preparations 
for promotion work. 
  Various specialized banks also have strengthened internal 
management to assign tasks to various levels, based on the 
responsibility system. They have extended business hours, so 
that buyers can buy treasury bonds at any sales point at any 
time they like. By 1 May, some sales points already had 
fulfilled their tasks. 

</TEXT>

