<F P=100> Central-South Region </F>
<H3> <TI>   Henan Reports First-Quarter Growth in Foreign Trade, Exports </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Henan Reports First-Quarter Growth in Foreign Trade, Exports </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   HK1005131294 Zhengzhou Henan People's Radio Network in 
Mandarin 1030 GMT 6 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> HK1005131294 </F>
<F P=104>  Zhengzhou Henan People's Radio Network </F>
<F P=105>  Mandarin </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Excerpt] Compared with the same period last year, our 
province's foreign trade and exports increased by a bigger 
margin in the first quarter this year. By the end of March, the 
province's overall export volume reached more than $310 million, 
an increase of 25.6 percent over the same period last year. 
  In the first quarter of this year, our province's foreign 
trade and exports had the following features: The export growth 
rates of various export enterprises were uneven. The export 
volumes of specialized companies in our province felld, whereas 
industrial and commercial exports at the prefectural and city 
levels rose by a bigger margin. The exports of foreign-funded 
enterprises maintained their strong growth. In the first 
quarter, foreign-funded enterprises' export volumes reached 
$37.44 million, registering an increase of 450 percent over the 
corresponding period last year. This margin of increase was much 
higher than the average growth rate of foreign-funded 
enterprises throughout the country. 
  With regard to the main countries and areas to which our 
province's products were exported, our exports to the 
traditional Hong Kong and Macao markets fell, while our exports 
to the EC countries increased fairly rapidly. [passage omitted 
including indistinct portion] 

</TEXT>

